      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SANDAVE STAPLES (7) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on her fast win the start prior, getting around this track over 457m in 25.36. Can return to winning form here if runs up to time two back. PRETTY POSH (1) was resuming when finishing fifth at this track in a Grade 5 (26.23). Has a good record here at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. SELECT AIRLEY (2) goes very well this trip starting 12 times for five wins and five minors. Placed last time (23.90) at Rockhampton in a Grade 4, finishing second and beaten 4.5 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SUTTON'S MAGIC (3) placed last time (25.73) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten 4.5 lengths. Has already won two times from this draw.",
